-To combine two or more list or collection we can use flatMap.

-StringJoiner => To join two or more strings
Ex:

class xyz
{
psvm(String[] args)
 {
   StringJoiner sj= new StringJoiner("&");
   sj.add("hello");
   sj.add("world");

  Sysout(sj);  //o/p => hello&world
 }
}

